            "dictionaryKey": "portal"
          },
          {
            "key": "research-bets",
            "intent": "lane",
            "implementation": "strategic or exploratory tracks",
            "dictionaryKey": "portal"
          },
          {
            "key": "archive-references",
            "intent": "lane",
            "implementation": "reference clusters and support areas",
            "dictionaryKey": "portal"
          }
        ],
        "markdown": "## How To Use This Board\n- Each visible workstream card is a portal consuming a summary owned by its source task graph.\n- Open any card to enter that workstream.\n- `Now` contains active implementation tracks.\n- `Foundations` holds reusable platform and graph-structure work.\n- `Product / UX` groups user-facing surface work.\n- `Research / Bets` keeps exploratory tracks reachable without crowding active delivery.\n- Child-track details live inside their parent graphs rather than on this root board.",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false,
        "identity": {
          "graphId": "tasks-root-manifest"
        }
      }
    },
